{"tid":1526824,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"15:30 機場特別交通消息","createTime":"2019-09-01T07:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T07:41:00.000Z","uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"02405dfbe18742dac913509f0bf02df9313821aa","tid":1526824,"uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:39:22.000Z","msg":"【特別交通消息】1/9/2019 (1530)<br />\n<br />\n因應機場的交通情況，龍運以下路線作出相應安排，乘客請依照在場外勤人員指示。<br />\n<br />\n暫停服務<br />\nS1、S64<br />\n<br />\n改道行駛<br />\nA線不經一號客運大樓、二號客運大樓、機場地面運輸中心。<br />\n所有A線加停港珠澳大橋香港口岸<br />\n<br />\nE32、E33、E33P、E34A、E34B、E41、E42不停以下各站<br />\n往機場方向<br />\n1.東涌消防局<br />\n2.東堤灣畔<br />\n3. 赤鱲角南路<br />\n4. 暢連路<br />\n5. 機場一號/二號客運大樓<br />\n6. 暢達路<br />\n7. 富豪機場酒店<br />\n8. 機場地面運輸中心<br />\n9. 機場博覽館站<br />\n<br />\n往新界方向<br />\n1. 機場博覽館<br />\n1. 機場地面運輸中心<br />\n2. 赤鱲角南路<br />\n3. 東涌纜車站<br />\n4. 東薈城/富東廣場<br />\n5. 裕東苑<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kmbhongkong/photos/a.695173743874065/2491763454215076/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkmbhongkong%2Fphotos%2Fa.695173743874065%2F2491763454215076%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2XxZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=85be0b6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kmbhongkong/photos/a.695173743874065/2491763454215076/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"efeae011631e33435e93f6917ea184f9254685af","tid":1526824,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd425adb5cd6c50900a744e718b625b4ab221f8","tid":1526824,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:41:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}